					Full Description



Bollente Companies, Inc. (Bollente), incorporated on March 7, 2008, operates through its subsidiary Bollente, Inc. Bollente manufactures and sells whole-house, electric tankless water heater. The Company's products include trutankless, truCirc and Vero. The Company also offers Vero, line of electric tankless water heaters.TrutanklessThe Company manufactures and distributes trutankless water heaters, a line of electric tankless water heaters. The Company's trutankless water heaters are designed to provide an endless hot water supply because they are designed to heat water as it flows through the system. Its trutankless product line utilizes the Company's Velix technology to heat water as it flows through the system. The Company launched MYtankless, a customizable online control panel for its trutankless line of electric water heaters. From the dashboard, residential and commercial users can obtain real-time status reports, adjust unit temperature settings, view approximately three years of water usage data and change notification settings from anywhere in the world, using a computer or Web-enabled smart device at www.mytankless.com. Its primary markets include Florida, Texas, Arizona and the rest of the Sunbelt region.truCirctruCirc is a high-tech water circulation pump. The truCirc can be used with its trutankless electric tankless water heater. truCirc's high-tech interface allows homeowners to change delivery modes or choose a zone or fixture to send hot water. Thermostatic shut-off valves can be installed at showerhead points of use throughout a home to eliminate wasted water.

